going to say the new rich text

00:10:19.110 --> 00:10:22.142
format, but I'm curious
about all of that

00:10:22.142 --> 00:10:23.850
to fix that, so we
can kind of say, like,

00:10:23.850 --> 00:10:27.360
no, no, we have something
even better than iMessage.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.860
DAVE BURKE: Yeah,
so super conscious

00:10:28.860 --> 00:10:31.727
of the iMessage situation.

00:10:31.727 --> 00:10:33.060
It depends on different regions.

00:10:33.060 --> 00:10:34.770
