00:15:37.040 --> 00:15:38.190
First is analytics.

00:15:38.190 --> 00:15:40.942
Obviously you know,
the web analytics space

00:15:40.942 --> 00:15:42.650
is pretty complex,
especially when you're

00:15:42.650 --> 00:15:43.995
doing SEO and things like that.

00:15:43.995 --> 00:15:46.370
So we've been working with a
