choice in terms of what things

00:17:10.968 --> 00:17:13.010
you want, but there's also
a distribution choice.

00:17:13.010 --> 00:17:15.890
And the different
technologies lend themselves

00:17:15.890 --> 00:17:18.300
to the distribution method
that your business is using.

00:17:18.300 --> 00:17:20.020
So that's why for
game developers who

00:17:20.020 --> 00:17:22.760
are used to a distribution model
that comes from an app store,

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:25.250
instant games is going to be
a much more natural choice

00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:27.710
from the distribution angle
as well as a technology angle.

00:17:27.710 --> 00:17:29.668
If you're a legacy is,
say, a shopping business

00:17:29.668 --> 00:17:31.610
and your legacy is
SEO and web, then

00:17:31.610 --> 00:17:33.380
you come from a
legacy of technologies

00:17:33.380 --> 00:17:35.840
