examples, Kotlin
first, Jetpack Compose,

00:20:41.560 --> 00:20:43.870
Navigation,
[INAUDIBLE] components,

00:20:43.870 --> 00:20:46.230
Flutter which is also
developed by Google,

00:20:46.230 --> 00:20:49.570
and just quickly
outdated tutorials.

00:20:49.570 --> 00:20:52.540
CHET HAASE: I'm not sure what
