00:27:02.960 --> 00:27:04.335
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:27:04.335 --> 00:27:05.127
CHET HAASE: Thanks.

00:27:05.127 --> 00:27:05.930
Hi.

00:27:05.930 --> 00:27:07.360
AUDIENCE: So, hello.

