is Google was actually the
first company, first tech

00:28:56.980 --> 00:29:00.320
company, to publish our
numbers on diversity.

00:29:00.320 --> 00:29:02.150
And I think that
was really amazing.

00:29:02.150 --> 00:29:04.150
Because then that kicked
off all other companies

00:29:04.150 --> 00:29:06.410
to do the same thing.

00:29:06.410 --> 00:29:08.350
And I think having
that transparency--

00:29:08.350 --> 00:29:10.690
There's a saying, sunshine
is the best disinfectant.

00:29:10.690 --> 00:29:12.610
Just looking at the
numbers, I think,

00:29:12.610 --> 00:29:15.950
causes people to be aware
and start to change.

00:29:15.950 --> 00:29:18.430
I think there's a lot of
opportunity for change, still,

00:29:18.430 --> 00:29:21.610
but it's been really amazing to
see especially on the Android

00:29:21.610 --> 00:29:26.030
team, is a lot of very
strong leaders, like Dianne,

00:29:26.030 --> 00:29:27.290
many people on the team.

00:29:27.290 --> 00:29:29.950
And yet I think it's a place
we can continue to invest.

00:29:29.950 --> 00:29:32.506
DAVE BURKE: The other thing
I would add is, you know,

00:29:32.506 --> 00:29:34.090
it actually makes
business sense.

00:29:34.090 --> 00:29:35.507
Like if you're
building a product,

00:29:35.507 --> 00:29:38.477
you want a diverse
set of opinions.

00:29:38.477 --> 00:29:40.060
You're going to build
better products.

00:29:40.060 --> 00:29:42.300
And just so from a
very fundamental level,

00:29:42.300 --> 00:29:43.300
it makes a lot of sense.

00:29:43.300 --> 00:29:44.320
You also have better teams.

00:29:44.320 --> 00:29:45.610
If you have a more
diverse set of teams

00:29:45.610 --> 00:29:47.110
and different
opinions, you're going

00:29:47.110 --> 00:29:49.720
have a better, healthier team.

00:29:49.720 --> 00:29:52.370
And so it's actually good for
business to do this as well.

00:29:52.370 --> 00:29:54.370
But you know, like I said,
I think this industry

00:29:54.370 --> 00:29:55.495
needs to work harder on it.

00:29:55.495 --> 00:29:58.650
And there's a couple of beacons
which I get excited about.

